<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Report on Agora Post</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 50px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="logo">
    <img src="https://d2w02n628dlis7.cloudfront.net/public/20250516/9ea7d25b323742b186fc658c74fe1818.png" alt="AIKA Logo">
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h2>There is a new feedback.</h2>
    <p>We have received a comment or feedback message from a user. The following is a summary:</p>

    <p><strong>Title: </strong> <span th:text="${feedbackType}">{Report type}</span></p>
    <p><strong>Issue ID: </strong> <span th:text="${issueId}">{Issue ID}</span></p>
    <p><strong>Username: </strong> <span th:text="${username}">{Username}</span></p>
    <p><strong>Feedback time: </strong> <span th:text="${feedbackTime}">{Created Time}</span></p>

    <p>You can check it via the AIKA Admin Panel:</p>
    <a th:href="${url}" class="button">View Feedback</a>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    <p>This email is automatically sent by the system. Please do not reply.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>